The '''Doaba Badlands''' was a vast [[Desert/Legends|desert]] on [[Socorro/Legends|Socorro]], covering almost three-quarters of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] surface. It was named for [[Iann Doaba]], a self-exiled warrior. During late dawn and early dusk, [[Min Min lights|mysterious lights]] were visible at the edge of the desert.

